{
  "texts": [
    "Upon inputting the 6W1H needs into the keyword extraction API, we obtained three keywords: \"diary,\" \"continue,\" and \"diary management service.\"",
    "Using these keywords to search the SUCCEED system, we found one case, as shown in Fig. 12.",
    "The search keywords were highlighted in the results.",
    "The discovered case pertained to an upcycling method that generates diaries through voice dialogue and facial recognition, supporting the innovative implementation of diary management services.Through the case study, it was discovered that developers can obtain user needs, service outlines, and development cases merely by facilitating a dialogue between users and a VA using the proposed method.",
    "From the perspective of users, the proposed method can be described as a technique that allows them to convey the outlines of the services they wish to be developed to developers simply through dialogue."
  ]
}